  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Observational study is to increase surveillance for breast and ovarian cancers, also to
      determine targeted risk-reducing and preventative strategies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The general design of this study is collecting data and reviewing the Principal
      Investigators' (P.I.) Standard Operating Procedures (SOP) on BRCA testing and changes made to
      their specific SOP.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
